physical_examinations.relevant_findings: Constitutional: NAD (No Acute Distress), Alert and oriented x 3; Cardiac: RRR (Regular Rate and Rhythm); Lungs: CTA (Clear to Auscultation); Abdomen: Soft, appropriate tenderness to palpation, no rebound tenderness/guarding; Wounds: CDI (Clean, Dry, Intact); Extremities: No CCE (Cyanosis, Clubbing, Edema).
